

NGUNIT

   This word used to be spelled with an apostrophe as nguni’t.
   ngunit
   but

   ngunit
   on the other hand

   Tinimbang Ka Ngunit Kulang
   (You Have Been Weighed and Found Wanting)
   1974 Filipino film by Lino Brocka, starring Christopher De Leon


   The word ngunit is a conjunction.

   The more colloquial Filipino word for ‘but’ in conversation is the
   Spanish pero.
